definition: Tsuen Wan district of New Territories, Hong Kong

sentences.english: We have arrived in Tsuen Wan, please exit from the train, thank you.
sentences.chinese: 本班列車已經抵達荃灣站，請所有乘客落車，多謝。

sentences.english: I still had to continue my uphill walk after taking the pictures to find the bus stop to take me back to Tsuen Wan.
sentences.chinese: 其後還要繼續步行到下一個巴士站才乘巴士回到荃灣。

sentences.english: Passenger may change there for MTR Tsuen Wan Line.
sentences.chinese: 乘客可在該站轉乘地鐵荃灣線。

sentences.english: Fountain of Life Animal Medical Center, G/F, 1 Tsuen Lok Street, Tsuen Wan, New Territories, Hong Kong.
sentences.chinese: 活泉動物醫療中心，香港九龍荃灣荃樂街1號地下。

sentences.english: At the end point Sham Tseng, you may take mini bus to Tsuen Wan MTR Station.
sentences.chinese: 終點爲深井，可在青龍頭青山公路乘車往荃灣或屯門。

sentences.english: The next station is Tsuen Wan West, please alight of the left.
sentences.chinese: 下一站系荃灣西，請用左邊車門落車。

sentences.english: Interchange station for the Island Line or Tsuen Wan Line.
sentences.chinese: 香港，乘客可以換乘港島線或荃灣線。

sentences.english: New Territories South Regional Police Headquarters 8Shing Mun Road, Tsuen Wan, N. T.
sentences.chinese: 新界，荃灣城門道八號，新界南總區警察總部。

sentences.english: Ajisen Ramen "Tsuen Wan Plaza " branch launching.
sentences.chinese: 味千拉麪荃灣廣場分店現已開業。

sentences.english: Tsuen Wan Shop at G41 Concord Square opened.
sentences.chinese: 於協和廣場荃灣店已正式開幕。

sentences.english: The train to Central is arriving. Please let passenger exit first.
sentences.chinese: 往荃灣列車即將到達，請先讓車上乘客落車。
